race.comment: PANTELONE (7) has been out of the winners list for a while but will find this easier than last start at Toowoomba. Placed only try here several starts ago and looks well placed returning with the claim. Expected to go close. DARK GLEAM (5) drew wide and sat four deep throughout when fading last time at Emerald. Winner the start prior and off a much better gate here is worth another try. DEPTH CHARGE (2) was safely held last time last time in richer company at Toowoomba. Will be prominent and give a sight this company. CAPO STRADA (1) is a local in great form. Won by a nose last time with more weight and should be tough to hold out again. FORTRESS AUSTRALIA (6) paced here last time. Has good pace and off the low draw will give a sight.
